===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# Understood only by a chosen few or an [[enlightened]] inner circle.
#: ''The writing in this manual is very '''esoteric'''; I need a degree in engineering just to understand it!
# Having to do with [[concept]]s that are highly [[theoretical]] and without obvious practical application; often with mystical or religious connotations.
# [[confidential|Confidential]]; [[private]].

